To install the KRE checkout the krl_install repository from:

  git@github.com:solargroovy/krl_install.git

Use the command:
  git clone git@github.com:solargroovy/krl_install.git

This will download the scripts and files necessary to install KRE.  

Detailed instructions are in the README.md file in the krl_install repository

The install process has been verified for 64 bit Centos 6.2
